31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有之前係咪成日捽眼？</blockquote><br />\n有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早排日日打黑痴同流鼻水<br />\n唔知傷風定鼻敏感，搞到隻眼成日腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d446731806532a674261ab9d0aa1a0d2c95233","tid":221800,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪隻眼成日都會痕好似有d水long long下咁眼皮邊會有d痴痴地既透明液體</blockquote><br />\n痕又唔痕既，但有層透明液體係眼球上球面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無乜眼膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前鼻敏感都試過出現呢層野，後尾唔知點解無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你應該係隻眼發炎<br />\n去睇醫生滴藥水啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇帶con?</blockquote><br />\n冇帶，視力無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能瞓教似啲枕頭整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f5455a2f8f3b84593fb3ef5ff49185dfe67a73","tid":221800,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"結膜炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我通常都係滴眼藥水再等雙眼休息多啲，瞓一覺會褪返啲"},{"pid":"0784b55c92f3110a968de7436b93134042588a19","tid":221800,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"相呢？"},{"pid":"fa32ecf13d662f83aebcad5f74033cd91d71cecf","tid":221800,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相呢？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/29/124152_02bf6336671f7d99bace3aa41e63adde.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F29%2F124152_02bf6336671f7d99bace3aa41e63adde.jpg